      "writtenOn": "2018-06-19T18:19:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Wrapped with transient errors in here.\n\nAs for 403, I don\u0027t think 403 here is fatal. IF it\u0027s really due to change of ACLs, next fetch of ref\u0027s HEAD will fail permanently due to 403, and we\u0027d be done.",
